@startuml
title Последовательность: создание отопительного устройства

actor User
participant DevicesApiController
participant DeviceCommandService
participant DeviceModelsRepository
participant DeviceRepository
participant MonolithClient
participant Monolith
database DevicesDB

User -> DevicesApiController: HTTP POST /devices {device payload}
DevicesApiController -> DeviceCommandService: createDevice(command)
DeviceCommandService -> DeviceModelsRepository: findDeviceModel(command.deviceModelId)
DeviceModelsRepository -> DevicesDB: SELECT device_types WHERE id = ?
DevicesDB --> DeviceModelsRepository: Тип устройства
DeviceModelsRepository --> DeviceCommandService: DeviceModel

DeviceCommandService -> DeviceRepository: saveNewDevice(command, deviceModel)
DeviceRepository -> DevicesDB: INSERT INTO devices(...)
DevicesDB --> DeviceRepository: OK
DeviceRepository --> DeviceCommandService: Device(id, ..., deviceModel)

alt устройство отопления (тип Heating relay)
  DeviceCommandService -> MonolithClient: registerHeatingDevice(Device)
  MonolithClient -> Monolith: HTTP POST /devices (информация об устройстве)
  Monolith --> MonolithClient: HTTP 201 {externalSensorId}
  MonolithClient --> DeviceCommandService: externalSensorId
  DeviceCommandService -> DeviceRepository: updateSensorExternalId(Device.id, externalSensorId)
  DeviceRepository -> DevicesDB: UPDATE devices SET sensor_external_id = externalSensorId WHERE id = Device.id
  DevicesDB --> DeviceRepository: OK
end

DeviceCommandService --> DevicesApiController: DeviceDto
DevicesApiController --> User: HTTP 201 JSON {device}

@enduml